es one chapter to applications of machine learning in image reconstruction. Based on college level in mathematics, physics, and engineering the textbook supports students in understanding the concepts. It is an essential reference for graduate students and engineers with electrical engineering and biomedical background due to its didactical structure and the balanced combination of methodologies and applications.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aAnalytische Inversion. 4aIterative Optimierung. 4aKlinische Anwendungen tomographischer Methoden. 4aMaschinelles Lernen. 4aTomographische Methoden. 7aSCIENCE / Physics / Optics & Light.2bisacsh  a.  aAnalytic Inversion.  aClinical Applications of Tomographic Methods.  aIterative Optimization.  aMachine Learning.  aTomography Methods.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chemistry, Mat.Sc, Geosc 2023 Englishz978311131923008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chemistry, Mat.Sc, Geosc 2023z9783111318660oZDB-23-DPC0 cEPUBz97831110557010 cprintz978311105503940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311105540440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783111055404423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783111055404/original  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  a978-3-11-131923-0  EBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chemistry, Mat.Sc, Geosc 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_CL_CHCOMSGSEN  aE